SEARCH
Package model.core

Class Country

java.lang.Object
model.core.Country
public class Country extends Object
Country represents a country with a name, money, population, resources, and people. It manages resources, people, and interactions with other countries.

    • Country

      public Country(String name, double initialMoney, long initialPopulation, Map<Resource,Integer> starterResources, Map<Resource,ResourceNodeDTO> ownedResources)
      Constructs a new Country.
      Parameters:
      name - the name of the country
      initialMoney - the initial amount of money, cannot be negative
      initialPopulation - the initial population, must be positive
      starterResources - the initial resources of the country
      ownedResources - the resources owned by the country
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if initialMoney is negative or initialPopulation is not positive
